 SetAPen grey220
  print If you
 setapen yellow240
  print  don't want to use a spell
 setapen grey220
  print  in your spellselection phase, just click the endturn gadget.
  print
  print
  print Be aware though that if you are playing with Texas Trash'em, you still
 setapen yellow240
  print  have to discard a spell.
